title: Renee Montoya - The Question
description:
Two stories from the pre 52 adventures of Renee Montoya as The Question. Pipeline is a compilation of The Question backup feature from Detective Comics. The Question #37 is part of the Blackest Night storyline.

Both are digital rips.

Cully Hamner's character design was well rationalised and made Renee Montoya a believable replacement for Vic Sage. Greg Rucka's characterizations of Tot and Renee fencing with philosophical quotes underscored the deeper philosophical underpinnings of their shared mission.
